title: 820-00165-A PP0V6 S0 DDRVTT @ 1.17v
message: i have a macbook air here. 820-00165-a. fan spins. no post. usb ligh working. i notice PP0V6 S0 DDRVTT is outputing 1.17V. is this generated from the rams?

title: 820-00165-A PP0V6 S0 DDRVTT @ 1.17v
message: just reviewed line. u7400 is ok. theres a cut line internally between pin 1 VTTSNS and pin 3 VTT.  jumped it and now its booting. :)
